about.author: Timo Homburg
about.comment: Egyptian Unicode Dictionary. Horizontally aligned character words are represented correctly. Vertically aligned and cube-assembled characters can currently not be represented in Unicode. They will be represented with there corresponding Codage sings between the unicode characters until this proposal has been adopted in Unicode.
